A4.text: Abu Dhabi is the UAE's second-most populous city, after Dubai.

A5.text: Abu Dhabi accounts for about two-thirds of the roughly $503 billion UAE economy.

A6.text: Sharjah is the third-most populous city in the United Arab Emirates, after Dubai and Abu Dhabi.
